  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carry Bart, an ex-gambler and professional monkey, towards his new fortune; the mythical \"Banana Springs,\" which is said to overflow with beautifully ripe banana bunches. Using both his hands and a considerable dose of patience, your task is to overcome the distance between Bart and the mountain's peak -- where Banana Springs lies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.poster.avif?t=1764960019\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.webm?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.mp4?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fully illustrated, 500ft tall mountain, with 15 distinct platforming sections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A complicated, dual joystick control scheme, that can be continually mastered over several playthroughs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A built in cooperative mode, for those who want to summit as a pair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Area specific gimmicks and music, that keep each new section unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dedicated cry button, for when you feel like sobbing your eyes out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many, many opportunities to fall back down to a previous section, with only one way back up...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/ede9bd477841bbc11a3e2d00ff22f893.poster.avif?t=1764960019\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/ede9bd477841bbc11a3e2d00ff22f893.webm?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/ede9bd477841bbc11a3e2d00ff22f893.mp4?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >(Inspired by \"Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy,\" and other games like it!)</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carry Bart, an ex-gambler and professional monkey, towards his new fortune; the mythical \"Banana Springs,\" which is said to overflow with beautifully ripe banana bunches. Using both his hands and a considerable dose of patience, your task is to overcome the distance between Bart and the mountain's peak -- where Banana Springs lies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.poster.avif?t=1764960019\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.webm?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845740/extras/3a52abedd15a647ca241b4798e2f3f4c.mp4?t=1764960019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fully illustrated, 500ft tall mountain, with 15 distinct platforming sections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A complicated, dual joystick control scheme, that can be continually mastered over several playthroughs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A built in cooperative mode, for those who want to summit as a pair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Area specific gimmicks and music, that keep each new section unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dedicated cry button, for when you feel like sobbing your eyes out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many, many opportunities to fall back down to a previous section, with only one way back up...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loo